text: Andrew Wilder (born July 5, 1990) is a former gridiron football punter who played for the Ottawa Redblacks of the Canadian Football League (CFL) in 2015. He played college football at Northern Arizona. ==Professional career== ===Tampa Bay Buccaneers=== Wilder was signed by the Tampa Bay Buccaneers on March 20, 2015. ==References== ==External links== *Tampa Bay Buccaneers bio *JustSportsStats.com bio Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Players of American football from Arizona Category:American football punters Category:Tampa Bay Buccaneers players Category:Ottawa Redblacks players
